{"tid":2514271,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"呢盒豆乳真係好鬼好飲","createTime":"2021-05-03T07:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T17:46:12.000Z","uid":188428,"like":69,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"7f841886ca987dba07ef5a51cc2412df4f85cf9f","tid":2514271,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZLeGpdtXaBBcnEfP2Pr3x11mkFbecseY7Mp5y3JMQCTx?filename=465chtv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F465chtv.jpg&h=00a4b2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔飲得真咖啡，會頭痛頭暈<br />\n但其實又好中意咖啡種香味<br />\n呢隻豆乳完全滿足到我需求<br />\n咖啡香味濃烈，叮熱嚟飲一流<br />\n<br />\n無咖啡因可以喪隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDonki $23.9, 759都有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08bf3ba4c8cac3a3a5094c2bc67332719517872e","tid":2514271,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":40,"score":-40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:02:48.000Z","msg":"幾多ml"},{"pid":"8a7bfa6d13b056810b98e32f473e60971b862de3","tid":2514271,"uid":201182,"like":33,"dislike":12,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"反而覺得好難飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我飲之前expect係維他麥精味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1546fce2fd4994283ef7cc3d7cdf33842e0a56","tid":2514271,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:04:28.000Z","msg":"有冇糖"},{"pid":"36faad44cb22676d5299a80b2823953a210d6f06","tid":2514271,"uid":306337,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"08bf3ba4c8cac3a3a5094c2bc67332719517872e","tid":2514271,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":40,"score":-40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:02:48